data.description: Do you dream of being in the mountains? Just so you can wander down a fern lined trail and listen to a meandering creek. Do you need a getaway from the hustle and bustle of everyday work life? Just so you can decompress. A long walk and a firepit can easily cure. Welcome to your own private State park!    This 4000 square foot home sits quaintly on 28 acres of groomed hardwoods , pastures and walking trails. Completely fenced in sitting on the highest point in Monroe County. Do you love entertaining? This home is perfect hosting an open floor plan with 16 foot pine ceilings with pine flooring throughout. Take in your surroundings from the loft with stainless steel cable railings overlooking a 6 foot paddle fan. This loft can be used as an office, guest area and even a kids pay area. The spacious master ensuite includes a soaking tub with picture window and also a custom tile shower. The walk out basement with windows on three sides is currently a state licensed hair salon. Equipped with separate hot water heater, HVAC, full bath, laundry and even bedroom/office space. But don't let that stop you this could easily become your dream theatre or man cave, just about anything your heart desired.     This home also offers a fully detached three car garage and fully equipped 860 square foot guest house. Moments away from Highfalls State Park and Indian Springs State Park take advantage of the income from short or long term renters through Air BNB. Or even rent as a full time apartment or , in law suite or guest house. The possibilities are endless, even a wedding venue.    As you pull up to the home you are greeted by the sound of trickling water in the courtyard from a water feature and waterfall. Ready for your Koi or Goldfish. The home and guest house are connected with new Trex decking along with all stainless steel cable railing for unobstructed views of the surrounding pastures and woods. By evening make it a romantic getaway for two observing the starlit sky from your personal hot tub.    The grounds include an 8x32 foot solar kiln with 4 fans along with a fully wired shipping container currently used for woodworking. The kiln can also be used as a green house for all you gardeners out there. The livestock are well cared for with a barn, wet weather pond, and a deep water well and county water provided. Don't forget about relaxing in your 24 foot above ground pool and very own sandy beach. Of course, after hiking by your creek with granite waterfall and exquisite plant life. For all you hunters out there you can be surrounded by wildlife just a step from you door.    This home has been meticulously maintained including exterior painting in 2021and interior in 2023. With high quality steel insulated doors and energy star double paned flip out windows. The mature landscaping can be enjoyed through these windows with transferable warranty.    Just minutes from 75 south and 1 hour from Atlanta. So why go to the mountains for a short vacation when you can call it home!
